					<source>The process of transforming data by using a cryptographic algorithm and key.</source>
				</segment>
			</unit>
			<unit id="115" translate="yes">
				<segment state="initial">
					<source>The transformed data can be recovered only by using the same algorithm and the same (symmetric) or related (public) key.</source>
